Founded in 1985, PPE made engineering innovations the
prime directive. Since the beginning our engineers improved
the horsepower and torque of the duramax diesel platform
with the PPE Duramaximizer.
PPE continued to innovate creating products to enhance and
improve the Duramax diesel platform, systematically finding
and improving “weak links” which would fail under the new
high horsepower and torque demands.
Our engineers built on their success by turning their sights on
Ford and Dodge diesel platforms. With each improvement,
they learned how to make clean, efficient power, while improv
ing fuel mileage and the drivers experience.

text.tspan: , PPE has expanded and is now focusing more than 30

g.text: years of experience to create a new line of intelligent,
heavy-duty upgrades for GM, Ford, Dodge/Ram, Jeep and
many others.
For use on smaller application only where "PACIFIC PERFORMANCE
ENGINEERING" loses legibility. For all other applications please use
original logo.
For use on dark background "PACIFIC PERFORMANCE ENGINEERING"
text may be inverted to white only.
